<lb n="0942a11" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0942a12" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0942a13" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 569</head>
<lb n="0942a14" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead>佛說心明經<note n="0942002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一卷〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一卷〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942002"><lem wit="【大】">一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0942a15" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0942a16" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">西晉<note n="0942003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">月氏國三藏＝三藏法師【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">月氏國三藏＝三藏法師【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942003"><lem wit="【大】">月氏國三藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">三藏法師</rdg></app>竺法護譯</byline>
<lb n="0942a17" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT14p0942a1701">聞如<app><lem wit="【CBETA】">是</lem><rdg wit="【大】">足</rdg></app>：</p><p id="pT14p0942a1704" place="inline">一時，佛遊王舍城靈鷲山，與五百比
<lb n="0942a18" ed="T"/>丘四部眾俱。佛以晨旦著衣持&CB00425;，往至一縣
<lb n="0942a19" ed="T"/>而行分衛，諸天龍神追於上侍，到梵志館門
<lb n="0942a20" ed="T"/>外而<note n="0942004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">住＋（分衛）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">住＋（分衛）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942004"><lem wit="【大】">住</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">住分衛</rdg></app>，佛放大光普炤十方。</p><p id="pT14p0942a2012" place="inline">時梵志婦執
<lb n="0942a21" ed="T"/>爨炊飯，見光照身身得安隱，解<note n="0942005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悍＝懌【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悍＝懌【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942005"><lem wit="【大】">悍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">懌</rdg></app>無量，心
<lb n="0942a22" ed="T"/>自念言：「今<note n="0942006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＝比【元】</note><app n="0942006"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">比</rdg></app>光耀，不似日月釋梵、四王諸天
<lb n="0942a23" ed="T"/>之明，躬荷熙怡不能自勝。」還顧見佛端正<note n="0942007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">殊＝姝【元】【明】</note><app n="0942007"><lem wit="【大】">殊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">姝</rdg></app>
<lb n="0942a24" ed="T"/>好，如星中月奇相巍巍，眾好具足諸根澹泊，
<lb n="0942a25" ed="T"/>無有衰入<note n="0942008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">建＝逮【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">建＝逮【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942008"><lem wit="【大】">建</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">逮</rdg></app>最上寂，得第一定<note n="0942009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如＝始【宮】</note><app n="0942009"><lem wit="【大】">如</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">始</rdg></app>日初出
<lb n="0942a26" ed="T"/>現<note n="0942010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">于＝乎【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0942010"><lem wit="【大】">于</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">乎</rdg></app>山崗，如轉輪王臨幸大殿<note n="0942011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">補＝寶【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">補＝寶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942011"><lem wit="【大】">補</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">寶</rdg></app>臣翼從，
<lb n="0942a27" ed="T"/>又若帝釋顯據忉利，猶梵天王於第七尊，如
<lb n="0942a28" ed="T"/>高山雪<note n="0942012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">冏＋（居永反）夾註【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0942012"><lem wit="【大】">冏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">冏<note place="inline">居永反</note></rdg></app>灼普現，倍加踊躍，重自<note n="0942013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惟忖＝忖惟【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惟忖＝忖惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942013"><lem wit="【大】">惟忖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">忖惟</rdg></app>：「今
<lb n="0942a29" ed="T"/>得&CB00418;佛及<note n="0942014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛＝眾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛＝眾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942014"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">眾</rdg></app>弟子，誠副宿願，欲以食饌奉進
<pb n="0942b" ed="T" id="T14.0569.0942b"/>
<lb n="0942b01" ed="T"/>正覺，隱察愚夫不信道德，志<note n="0942015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">在＝存【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">在＝存【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942015"><lem wit="【大】">在</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">存</rdg></app>邪疑六十
<lb n="0942b02" ed="T"/>二見，見<note n="0942016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妾＝我【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妾＝我【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942016"><lem wit="【大】">妾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">我</rdg></app>所施必興結恨，宿命愆咎失雄
<lb n="0942b03" ed="T"/>猛男，嬰墜女像羈制於人，欲施聖尊不得由
<lb n="0942b04" ed="T"/>已，宜順護意當如之何？」便即<note n="0942017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">箄＝捍【宋】，壓【元】【明】，捭【宮】</note><note n="0942017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">箄＝捍【宋】，＝壓【元】【明】，＝捭【宮】</note><app n="0942017"><lem wit="【大】">箄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">捍</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">壓</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">捭</rdg></app>飯取汁一杓
<lb n="0942b05" ed="T"/>以用上佛。佛之威神，&CB00425;中自然有百味食，佛
<lb n="0942b06" ed="T"/>時達嚫，口歎頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0942b07" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT14p0942b0701" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「假以馬百疋，</l><l>金銀挍鞍勒，</l>
<lb n="0942b08" ed="T"/><l>用惠施於人，</l><l>不如杓飯汁。</l>
<lb n="0942b09" ed="T"/><l>設以七寶車，</l><l>載滿諸<note n="0942018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">珍琦＝琦珍【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">珍琦＝琦珍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942018"><lem wit="【大】">珍琦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">琦珍</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0942b10" ed="T"/><l>杓飯汁施佛，</l><l>其福過於彼。</l>
<lb n="0942b11" ed="T"/><l>若施白象百，</l><l>明珠瓔珞飾，</l>
<lb n="0942b12" ed="T"/><l>供佛一杓汁，</l><l>其福超彼上。</l>
<lb n="0942b13" ed="T"/><l>如聖轉輪王，</l><l>普賢玉女后，</l>
<lb n="0942b14" ed="T"/><l>端正無有比，</l><l>七寶瓔珞身。</l>
<lb n="0942b15" ed="T"/><l>如是之妙類，</l><l>其數各有百，</l>
<lb n="0942b16" ed="T"/><l>悉以配施人，</l><l>不如一杓汁。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0942b17" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0942b1701">於時，梵志靜住而聽，聞佛所歎，心懷疑惑，前
<lb n="0942b18" ed="T"/>問佛言：「一杓飯汁何所直也，而乃稱讚？若干
<lb n="0942b19" ed="T"/>寶施象馬車乘，不可<note n="0942019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">呰毀＝訾數【元】，言數【明】</note><note n="0942019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呰毀＝訾數【元】，＝言數【明】</note><app n="0942019"><lem wit="【大】">呰毀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">訾數</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">言數</rdg></app>，而云不如杓飯汁
<lb n="0942b20" ed="T"/>施，斯之飯汁不直一錢，然乃咨嗟若干億倍，
<lb n="0942b21" ed="T"/>孰當信哉？」</p>
<lb n="0942b22" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0942b2201">於是，世尊尋即顯露廣長之舌，以覆其面上
<lb n="0942b23" ed="T"/>至梵天，告梵志曰：「吾從無數億百千劫，常
<lb n="0942b24" ed="T"/>行至誠六度無極，施諸所安有而不惜乃獲
<lb n="0942b25" ed="T"/>斯舌，寧以妄語能致之乎？吾欲問，卿至誠答
<lb n="0942b26" ed="T"/>之。曾頗往返舍衛羅閱，中路<note n="0942020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（見）＋有【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（見）＋有【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942020"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">見有</rdg></app>樹名尼拘
<lb n="0942b27" ed="T"/>類，蔭庇人眾五百乘車<note n="0942021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乎＝不【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乎＝不【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942021"><lem wit="【大】">乎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">不</rdg></app>？」</p><p id="pT14p0942b2711" place="inline">對曰：「唯然，有是
<lb n="0942b28" ed="T"/><note n="0942022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔樹我〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔樹我〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942022"><lem wit="【大】">樹，我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>所見也。」</p><p id="pT14p0942b2806" place="inline">世尊又問：「其子大如？」</p><p id="pT14p0942b2814" place="inline">答曰：「形
<lb n="0942b29" ed="T"/>如芥子。」</p><p id="pT14p0942b2904" place="inline">佛告梵志：「卿真兩舌，實如芥子，樹何
<pb n="0942c" ed="T" id="T14.0569.0942c"/>
<lb n="0942c01" ed="T"/><note n="0942023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">巨乎＝巨大【宋】【宮】，大乎【元】【明】</note><note n="0942023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">巨乎＝巨大【宋】【宮】，＝大乎【元】【明】</note><app n="0942023"><lem wit="【大】">巨乎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">巨大</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">大乎</rdg></app>？」</p><p id="pT14p0942c0103" place="inline">對曰：「審爾，不敢欺也。」</p><p id="pT14p0942c0111" place="inline">佛又告曰：「種如
<lb n="0942c02" ed="T"/>芥子，生樹廣大，地之生<note n="0942024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">殖＝植【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">殖＝植【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942024"><lem wit="【大】">殖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">植</rdg></app>適無所置所覆彌
<lb n="0942c03" ed="T"/>廣，乃<note n="0942025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">況＝爾況復【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">況＝爾況復【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942025"><lem wit="【大】">況</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">爾況復</rdg></app>如來、無上至真等正覺，無量福會普
<lb n="0942c04" ed="T"/>勝者哉！戒、定、慧、<note n="0942026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">解脫＝脫脫【宋】【元】，解度【宮】</note><note n="0942026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">解脫＝脫脫【宋】【元】，＝解度【宮】</note><app n="0942026"><lem wit="【大】">解脫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">脫脫</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">解度</rdg></app>、<note n="0942027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔解脫〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔解脫〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942027"><lem wit="【大】">解脫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>知見事，大慈弘
<lb n="0942c05" ed="T"/>哀無所不濟，以饌供獻<note n="0942028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">功＝福【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">功＝福【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942028"><lem wit="【大】">功</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">福</rdg></app>祚難計。」梵志默然
<lb n="0942c06" ed="T"/>無以加報。</p><p id="pT14p0942c0605" place="inline">時佛乃笑，五色光從口出，照十方
<lb n="0942c07" ed="T"/>五趣之類，<note n="0942029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天＝夫【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0942029"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">夫</rdg></app>欲<note n="0942030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">止＝至【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">止＝至【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942030"><lem wit="【大】">止</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">至</rdg></app>、人心喜、餓鬼<note n="0942031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飽＋（滿）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飽＋（滿）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942031"><lem wit="【大】">飽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">飽滿</rdg></app>、地獄
<lb n="0942c08" ed="T"/>痛息、畜生意開罪除，尋光來詣佛所。諸佛
<lb n="0942c09" ed="T"/>笑法皆有常瑞，授菩薩決，遍照十方光從頂
<lb n="0942c10" ed="T"/>入；授緣覺&CB00028;，光入面門；授聲聞&CB00028;，光入肩斗；
<lb n="0942c11" ed="T"/>說生天事，光從&CB00685;入；說降人中，光從膝入；說
<lb n="0942c12" ed="T"/>趣三苦，<note n="0942032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（光）＋從【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（光）＋從【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942032"><lem wit="【大】">從</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">光從</rdg></app>足心入。</p><p id="pT14p0942c1208" place="inline">諸佛之欣，不以欲笑，不
<lb n="0942c13" ed="T"/>以瞋笑，不以癡笑，不放逸笑，不利欲笑，不
<lb n="0942c14" ed="T"/>榮貴笑，不富饒笑，今佛普等愍傷群萌，行
<lb n="0942c15" ed="T"/>大慈笑無斯七也。</p><p id="pT14p0942c1508" place="inline">賢者阿難分別七法，知法
<lb n="0942c16" ed="T"/>解義曉時了節暢眾會事，<note n="0942033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自＝思【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">自＝思【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942033"><lem wit="【大】">自</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">思</rdg></app>省己身明眾人
<lb n="0942c17" ed="T"/>根，即從座起，更整衣服，長跪問佛：「佛何<note n="0942034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">因＋（緣）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">因＋（緣）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942034"><lem wit="【大】">因</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">因緣</rdg></app>
<lb n="0942c18" ed="T"/>笑？願說其意。」</p><p id="pT14p0942c1806" place="inline">佛告阿難：「見梵志婦發大意乎？」</p>
<lb n="0942c19" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0942c1901">對曰：「已見。」</p><p id="pT14p0942c1905" place="inline">佛言：「斯婦壽終，當轉女像<note n="0942035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得＝後【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得＝後【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942035"><lem wit="【大】">得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">後</rdg></app>為
<lb n="0942c20" ed="T"/>男子，生于天上諸天中尊，下生世間為人中
<lb n="0942c21" ed="T"/>上，解深妙法如幻如化、如水中月影響野馬，
<lb n="0942c22" ed="T"/>&CB00230;三十劫當得作佛，名曰心明如來、至真、等
<lb n="0942c23" ed="T"/>正覺、明行成為、善逝、世間解、無上士、道法御、天
<lb n="0942c24" ed="T"/>人師，號佛、世尊。」</p><p id="pT14p0942c2407" place="inline">梵志心伏，五體投地剋心自
<lb n="0942c25" ed="T"/>責，懺曰：「我如小兒愚癡闇冥，懷疑猶豫不識
<lb n="0942c26" ed="T"/>大聖，口出&CB00308;言唯原罪釁。」</p><p id="pT14p0942c2611" place="inline">佛言：「善哉！善哉！若
<lb n="0942c27" ed="T"/>自見過歸命於佛，於道法律悔殃塵者，其咎
<lb n="0942c28" ed="T"/>損<note n="0942036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">減＝滅【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">減＝滅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942036"><lem wit="【大】">減</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">滅</rdg></app>、福增日滋。」</p><p id="pT14p0942c2807" place="inline">梵志<note n="0942037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">進啟＝啟進【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">進啟＝啟進【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942037"><lem wit="【大】">進啟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">啟進</rdg></app>：「唯垂大哀！加恩
<lb n="0942c29" ed="T"/>矜攝令得出家。」佛即納受以為沙門，鬚髮則
<pb n="0943a" ed="T" id="T14.0569.0943a"/>
<lb n="0943a01" ed="T"/>除法衣在身。於時，世尊講四聖諦苦<note n="0943001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">習＝集【元】【明】</note><app n="0943001"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>盡
<lb n="0943a02" ed="T"/>道，梵志踊躍漏盡意解。</p><p id="pT14p0943a0210" place="inline">佛說如是，賢者阿難、
<lb n="0943a03" ed="T"/>諸四部眾、天人龍神，皆發道意，歡喜<note n="0943002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">稽首＋（而退）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0943002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">稽首＋（而退）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0943002"><lem wit="【大】">稽首</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">稽首而退</rdg></app>。</p></div1>
<lb n="0943a04" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>佛說心明經</jhead></juan>
</body></text></TEI.2>
